05:56.197 --> 05:58.081
I read the last
stack of books.

05:58.083 --> 06:00.367
No questions... asked.

06:00.369 --> 06:04.371
But, uh, Jeremy Bentham is
a utilitarian philosopher.

06:04.373 --> 06:06.540
That has nothing to do
with being a detective.

06:06.542 --> 06:08.992
Bentham is the father
of modern criminology.

06:08.994 --> 06:11.828
He said that crime is
the result of free will.

06:13.132 --> 06:14.965
Uh, you're gonna put
the acid away

06:14.967 --> 06:16.833
before we answer the door,
right?

06:21.689 --> 06:24.141
Delivery for you,
Mr. Holmes.

06:24.143 --> 06:26.977
Thank you, Crabtree,
but I'm afraid I...

06:26.979 --> 06:28.645
Oh, my God.

06:28.647 --> 06:30.180
Is that...?

06:30.182 --> 06:32.282
A bee in a box?
Yes, it is.

06:32.284 --> 06:34.868
Fairly unimpressive
as far as bribes go.

06:34.870 --> 06:38.405
Not if you're
an apiculturist.

06:38.407 --> 06:42.743
That's an osmia avoseta--
solitary bee

06:42.745 --> 06:45.862
famed for building exquisite
nests from flower petals.

06:47.665 --> 06:50.200
It's on the verge
of extinction.

06:50.202 --> 06:53.369
Crabtree, this is exquisite.

06:53.371 --> 06:54.721
I cannot accept it.

06:54.723 --> 06:57.557
Please tell Mr. Lydon
not to contact me again.

06:57.559 --> 07:00.010
I told him you are a man
of convictions.

07:00.012 --> 07:02.596
Perhaps now
he'll believe me.

07:14.325 --> 07:16.743
This is ridiculous.
Single stick is <i>your</i> hobby.

07:16.745 --> 07:18.561
It's not gonna help me
solve crimes.

07:19.998 --> 07:21.782
Aim for the pate.

07:21.784 --> 07:23.399
Good morning, Captain.

07:23.401 --> 07:25.869
Are you in bed with
a guy named Gerald Lydon?

07:25.871 --> 07:27.504
He tried to hire me.
I declined.

07:27.506 --> 07:29.089
Well, that's not what he thinks.

07:29.091 --> 07:31.258
You should get down here.
He's asking for you.

07:31.260 --> 07:32.709
Why?

07:32.711 --> 07:35.545
I don't know,
but we just arrested him.

07:35.547 --> 07:39.132
He shot his driver--
guy named Crabtree.

07:39.134 --> 07:42.035
He's being charged with murder.

07:42.829 --> 07:46.829
<font color=#00FF00>♪ Elementary 1x17 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Possibility Two</font>
